column1: applied "filter" row 19, in column "variant" select text filter, chose equal="base" AND ( "MB786" OR "MB786/STM324") with /EN or /WS  depending if encryption and socket are needed
With "Base " AND "MB786" you will have the MB786 BOM, for STM32F207 (mangusta witout encryption) without socket
With "Base " AND "MB786/EN" you will have the MB786 BOM, for STM32F217 (Mangusta with encryption) without socket
With "Base " AND "MB786/JAVA" you will have the MB786 BOM, for STM32F207 (mangusta witout encryption) without socket and with JAVA demo
With "Base " AND "MB786/STM324" you will have the MB786 BOM, for STM32F407 (manta without encryption) without socket
With "Base " AND "MB786/STM324/EN" you will have the MB786 BOM, for STM32F417 (Manta with encryption) without socket
With "Base " AND "MB786/WS" you will have the MB786 BOM, for STM32F207 (mangusta without encryption) with socket
With "Base " AND "MB786/EN/WS" you will have the MB786 BOM, for STM32F217 (Mangusta with encryption) with socket
With "Base " AND "MB786/STM324/WS" you will have the MB786 BOM, for STM32F407 (manta without encryption) with socket
With "Base " AND "MB786/STM324/EN/WS" you will have the MB786 BOM, for STM32F417 (Manta with encryption) with socket
With "Base " AND "MB786/STM324/MP3" you will have the MB786 BOM, for STM32F407 (Manta with MP3 audio) without socket
With "Base " AND "MB786/STM324/IPOD" you will have the MB786 BOM, for STM32F407 (Manta with MFI authentification chip fitted) without socket
With "Base " AND "MB786/STM324/JAVA" you will have the MB786 BOM, for STM32F407 (Manta with JAVA demo) without socket
